			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The recipes for the items include:<BR>
Broom of Trilon- Star Ruby, griffon feather not griffin feather, broom, and cyclops toes<BR>
Shovel of Pronz- Ruby, gargoyle eye, shovel, hill giant toes<BR>
Stein of Ulissa- Sapphire, mermaid scale, stein, ice giant toes<BR>
Torch of Alna- Fire emerald, fire drake scale, torch, fire giant toes<BR>
<BR>
Give all of these items to Vira at the temple of Soulsek Ro and you will be awarded the items and a bit of exp<BR>
<BR>
The items increase the level, strength, and endurance of the pets, as well as the casting time and size. The effects of the items are immediate but it really takes effect on level 20+ pets. So, in other words, your lower level pets will be affected, but the 20+ pets really get affected. <BR>
So, there you have it, the low-down on the focus items. I would tell you all where to find the items, but I'm too mean ;P<BR>
<BR>
Arizel Darkcaster,<BR>
Conjurer of the 14th season,<BR>
